Bxb2 11. Rb1 Bf6 { Having the e7-pawn protected will help in a few lines. } 12.
Nd4 { With correct play, this is just a draw. } 12... Qxa2 13. Nxc6 bxc6 14.
Bxc6 { Allows Black to get a good position. } 14... Bh3 15. Bxa8 Rxa8 16. Re1
Bc3 { We will eventually cash in the exchange, with a fine game. } *

