11. cxd5 cxd5 12. Nxd5 g5 { Forcing a clarification in the center. } 13. Nxf6+
Bxf6 14. Bf2 Qa5+ 15. Kf1 Nc6 16. Nxc6 bxc6
{ The open character of the position, and the sad king on f1, give us plenty of play for the pawn. }
