6. Nbd2 d6 { Fighting against the white center is very topical here. } 7. exd6
O-O 8. a3 Nxd2
{ We're forced into this trade, but our development edge is going to carry us. }
9. axb4 Nxf3+ 10. Qxf3 Re8+ 11. Be2 Nc6
