{ This is a very sharp position, but we're doing quite well after both  13.Nb1  e5  and @@StartFEN@@r1b1k2r/1p1n1pp1/p3pn1p/2q5/1b1NP2B/2N1Q3/PPP3PP/2KR1B1R w kq - 4 13@@EndFEN@@  13.Nd5!?  exd5  14.a3  Ba5  15.b4  Qe7  . }
