{ We are happy to see White's dark-squared bishop getting traded for ours since the pawn on c3 blocked the radius of the g7-bishop. }
9... Bxe5 10. Nxe5 Qc7 11. Nef3 Nc6 12. O-O Nf6
{ We intend ...Bf5 and ...Rfd8 next, with a preferable game. } *

