cxd4 O-O 8. Nc3 Nc6 9. Qd2 d6
{ If  10.h3  , we're doing quite well after both the more concrete  10...e5  or the slower  10...Bg7  ,  followed perhaps by ...a6, ...b5, ...Bb7 etc. }
