{ Structurally, Black's position is already to be preferred   @@StartBracket@@the extremely awkward Nc3 has much to do with that@@EndBracket@@. }
11... h6 12. Bf4 Bb4
{ It's quite a mess, but the kind of a mess we should be happy with, I believe. }
