{ Our center exerts a lot of pressure. } 6. Bb5+ Nc6 7. Ne2 Rg8
{ If we're castling anywhere, it's queenside, making this move a very useful resource in most positions. For instance  8.O-O  Qb6  is not an improvement either. }
*

