{ For those of you looking for a very messy and unbalanced positions to play, I would recommend }
8... Bg7 { here. } 9. Ne2 O-O
{ I like this better than  9...f5  −  by unpinning the Nc6, we're forcing White to spend a tempo on a3 instead of  10.Nd4  ,  which would have been the reply in case of 9...f5. }
