{ 10...e3!?  is also very playable, but perhaps we don't need to do it yet. It's definitely an idea White needs to monitor at all times, though. }
11. c4 { And now, a forced sequence of moves follows. } 11... Nxd4 12. Bxd4
dxc4 13. bxc4 Bg4 14. Nc3 Rc8 { Black is doing very well. } *

