12... Rxd1+ 13. Rxd1 Bd7 { No need to even consider accepting that sacrifice. }
14. Nd2 Bxa4
{ There is humor in chess! The position is a mirrored image ofthis one, but with colors reversed. After  15.Nxe4  Bxc2  16.Nxf6+  Bxf6  17.Rd2  , the game is equal − the queenside will disappear soon. }
