1. f4
{ The fabled reversed Dutch. Turns out even a tempo-up Dutch is still not great, who could have known. }
1... d5 2. Nf3 c5 3. g3
{ Most people play the Bird with the intention of playing the tempo up Leningrad, but we'll take a brief look at the other options, too. }
3... g6 4. Bg2 Bg7 5. O-O Nc6 6. d3
